 {\displaystyle {\mathcal {S}}={T \over 2}\int \mathrm {d} ^{2}\sigma {\sqrt {-h}}h^{ab}g_{\mu \nu }(X)\partial _{a}X^{\mu }(\sigma )\partial _{b}X^{\nu }(\sigma )}
 where 
 
 
 
 T
 
 
 {\displaystyle T}
 is the string tension, 
 
 
 
 
 g
 
 μ
 ν
 
 
 
 
 {\displaystyle g_{\mu \nu }}
 is the metric of the target manifold, 
 
 
 
 
 h
 
 a
 b
 
 
 
 
 {\displaystyle h_{ab}}
 is the worldsheet metric, 
 
 
 
 
